---
import Layout from "../../layouts/Layout.astro";
import "../../styles/globals.css";
import { Header } from "../../components/Header";
import InnerPageCTA from "../../components/InnerPageCTA.astro";
import Footer from "../../components/Footer.astro";

const b = import.meta.env.BASE_URL;
---

<Layout
  title="Guide to Branded Tracking Pages - parcelLab"
  description="Learn how branded tracking pages benefit both customers and businesses, from reducing inquiries to building personalized post-purchase experiences."
>
  <Header client:load />
  <main>
    <!-- Article Header -->
    <section class="section-generous">
      <div class="mx-auto max-w-[1440px] px-6 md:px-12">
        <div class="mx-auto max-w-[800px]">
          <a href={`${b}/blog/`} class="group mb-8 inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-sm font-medium text-[var(--ink-muted)] transition-colors hover:text-[#3D3AD3]">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="transition-transform group-hover:-translate-x-0.5"><path d="M19 12H5"/><path d="m12 19-7-7 7-7"/></svg>
            Back to blog
          </a>
          <span class="mb-4 inline-block rounded-full bg-[#3D3AD3]/10 px-3 py-1 text-xs font-semibold text-[#3D3AD3]">Post-Purchase</span>
          <h1 class="text-display text-[var(--ink)]">Guide to Branded Tracking Pages</h1>
          <div class="mt-6 flex items-center gap-4 text-sm text-[var(--ink-muted)]">
            <span>By <strong class="font-medium text-[var(--ink-secondary)]">Anna Lapezo</strong></span>
            <span class="h-1 w-1 rounded-full bg-[var(--ink-muted)]"></span>
            <time datetime="2023-08-28">August 28, 2023</time>
            <span class="h-1 w-1 rounded-full bg-[var(--ink-muted)]"></span>
            <span>6 min read</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Article Body -->
    <section class="pb-16 md:pb-24">
      <div class="mx-auto max-w-[800px] px-6 md:px-12">
        <p class="text-[var(--ink-secondary)] leading-relaxed text-lg">
          In today's digital marketplace, consumers expect instant access to information. While brands historically built identity through physical stores and staff, contemporary e-commerce requires new approaches to stand out. Recent research reveals that 90% of people want brands to engage them during delivery, with 56% demanding immediate delay notifications.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-heading text-[var(--ink)] mt-12 mb-4">What is a Branded Tracking Page?</h2>
        <p class="text-[var(--ink-secondary)] leading-relaxed">
          A branded tracking page leverages customer names and tracking numbers to display real-time order information in a personalized dashboard. Crucially, the brand hosts this directly rather than relying on third-party carriers.
        </p>
        <p class="text-[var(--ink-secondary)] leading-relaxed mt-4">
          Key design features include:
        </p>
        <ul class="mt-4 space-y-3">
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#3D3AD3" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="mt-0.5 shrink-0"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="1"/></svg>
            <span class="text-[var(--ink-secondary)]">Real-time delivery updates (graphics, written notifications, or live maps)</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#3D3AD3" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="mt-0.5 shrink-0"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="1"/></svg>
            <span class="text-[var(--ink-secondary)]">Personalized content reflecting customer preferences</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#3D3AD3" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="mt-0.5 shrink-0"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="1"/></svg>
            <span class="text-[var(--ink-secondary)]">Links to branded materials and related products</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#3D3AD3" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="mt-0.5 shrink-0"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="1"/></svg>
            <span class="text-[var(--ink-secondary)]">Design consistency with brand guidelines</span>
          </li>
        </ul>

        <h2 class="text-heading text-[var(--ink)] mt-12 mb-4">How Branded Tracking Pages Benefit Customers</h2>
        <p class="text-[var(--ink-secondary)] leading-relaxed">
          Research indicates 57% of people admit to being emotionally tied to online purchases, with 63% finding fulfillment and delivery processes most emotionally significant.
        </p>

        <div class="mt-6 space-y-6">
          <div class="rounded-xl border border-[var(--line)] bg-[var(--surface-raised)] p-6">
            <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-[var(--ink)]">All Information in One View</h3>
            <p class="mt-2 text-[var(--ink-secondary)] leading-relaxed">
              Real-time updates directly from the brand eliminate the need to visit multiple carrier sites, reducing confusion and anxiety.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="rounded-xl border border-[var(--line)] bg-[var(--surface-raised)] p-6">
            <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-[var(--ink)]">Up-Sell/Cross-Sell Opportunities</h3>
            <p class="mt-2 text-[var(--ink-secondary)] leading-relaxed">
              Personalized product recommendations on tracking pages introduce customers to relevant items at a moment of high engagement.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="rounded-xl border border-[var(--line)] bg-[var(--surface-raised)] p-6">
            <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-[var(--ink)]">Building Connection</h3>
            <p class="mt-2 text-[var(--ink-secondary)] leading-relaxed">
              Direct brand relationship throughout delivery eliminates customer disconnection when third parties take over communications.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <h2 class="text-heading text-[var(--ink)] mt-12 mb-4">How Branded Order Status Pages Benefit Brands</h2>

        <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-[var(--ink)] mt-8 mb-3">Send Targeted Updates</h3>
        <p class="text-[var(--ink-secondary)] leading-relaxed">
          Customizable tracking pages enable automated, targeted communications. 42% of people will unsubscribe from a brand's marketing content if it is targeted incorrectly, making relevance essential. Brands report improved open rates, click-through rates, and increased traffic.
        </p>

        <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-[var(--ink)] mt-8 mb-3">Reduce Customer Inquiries</h3>
        <p class="text-[var(--ink-secondary)] leading-relaxed">
          Offering a branded tracking page is known to reduce customer inquiries by up to 25%. Instant order information accessibility decreases support calls, while FAQ links or preferred contact channels manage remaining inquiries efficiently.
        </p>

        <div class="my-10 rounded-2xl bg-[var(--surface-sunken)] p-8">
          <p class="text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.1em] text-[var(--ink-muted)]">Key Stat</p>
          <p class="mt-2 text-lg font-medium text-[var(--ink)]">Branded tracking pages reduce customer inquiries by up to 25% while increasing return traffic and engagement.</p>
        </div>

        <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-[var(--ink)] mt-8 mb-3">Build Personalized Experiences</h3>
        <p class="text-[var(--ink-secondary)] leading-relaxed">
          Custom pages create recognizable brand experiences, replacing generic carrier communications with familiar updates that strengthen customer loyalty.
        </p>

        <div class="my-12 border-t border-[var(--line)]"></div>

        <p class="text-[var(--ink-secondary)] leading-relaxed">
          parcelLab serves as the world's leading post-purchase experience platform, translating operational data into customized customer experiences. The platform enables brands to deliver proactive, personalized updates across delivery confirmations, returns, and parcel tracking -- transforming routine operational moments into meaningful relationship-building opportunities.
        </p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <InnerPageCTA />
  </main>
  <Footer />
</Layout>
